ame></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01876">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 15. 9. 1909</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01878">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 21. 9. 1909</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01876">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 15. 9. 1909</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01882">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 27. 10. 1909</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
